"hidden\" name=\"locale\" value=\"en-gb\" id=\"locale\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"js\" value=\"1\" id=\"js\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"css\" value=\"1\" id=\"css\"> <button class=\"s-b-button\" aria-live=\"polite\" aria-labelledby=\"sb1-label\" type=\"submit\" tabindex=\"\" aria-pressed=\"false\" id=\"sb1\"> <span class=\"s-b-icon s-b-s\"> <i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"gelicon gelicon--share s-b-gelicon\"></i> </span>  <span id=\"sb1-label\" class=\"s-b-labels\"> <span class=\"s-b-label s-b-s\" role=\"presentation\">Share</span> <span class=\"s-b-label-long s-b-s\" role=\"presentation\">this page</span> <span class=\"s-b-hidden\" role=\"presentation\">This page has been Shared 34 times</span> </span> </button> </form> </span> <span class=\"s-b-panel  s-b-p-auto\" id=\"sb1-panel\" data-variant=\"light\"> <span class=\"s-b-pointer\"></span> <p>Share this with</p> <ul class=\"s-b-p-networks\">  <li> <a href=\"http://digg.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fguides%2Fzwxbjxs&title=Why%20do%20we%20remember%20the%20poets%20and%20not%20the%20composers%20of%20WW1%3F&bodytext=Sara%20Mohr-Pietsch%20looks%20at%20the%20composers%2C%20such%20as%20Vaughan%20Williams%20and%20Ivor%20Gurney%2C%20whose%20work%20was%20influenced%20by%20their%20service%20in%20World%20War%20One.\" target=\"_blank\" data-window-width=\"900\" data-window-height=\"560\" data-network=\"digg\" tabindex=\"\" class=\"s-b-p-a\"> <span> <i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"gelicon gelicon--digg\"></i> </span> Digg  </a> </li>  <li> <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fguides%2Fzwxbjxs\" target=\"_blank\" data-window-width=\"626\" data-window-height=\"236\" data-network=\"facebook\" tabindex=\"\" class=\"s-b-p-a\"> <span> <i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"gelicon gelicon--facebook\"></i> </span> Facebook  </a> </li>  <li> <a href=\"https://plus.google.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fguides%2Fzwxbjxs\" target=\"_blank\" data-window-width=\"550\" d