n></div><div class=\"context\"><span class=\"genre k-type-body-index\">History</span><p class=\"title\n                            k-type-header\">How did Pack Up Your Troubles become the viral hit of WW1?</p></div><div class=\"connection\"><p class=\"k-type-body-index\"><img src=\"http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/80x80/p01q27db.jpg\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"type\">Presented by</span><span class=\"name\">Gareth Malone</span></p></div></a></div><div class=\"\n                k-promo promo-3 iwonder\n                    k-colour-palette-palette-2\"><a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/guides/zws9xnb\"><div class=\"media\"><img class=\"resp square\" src=\"http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/256x256/p01s8j9y.jpg\" data-pid=\"p01s8j9y\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"overlay\"></span></div><div class=\"context\"><span class=\"genre k-type-body-index\">Arts &amp; Culture</span><p class=\"title\n                            k-type-header\">Did Oh What a Lovely War shape our view of WW1?</p></div></a></div><div class=\"\n                k-promo promo-4 gel\"><a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p01n6nr7\"><div class=\"media\"><img class=\"resp widescreen\" src=\"http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/256x144/p01ntdhv.jpg\" data-pid=\"p01ntdhv\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"k-g-sprite icon k-video\">Watch</span><span class=\"overlay\"></span></div><div class=\"context\"><span class=\"genre k-type-body-index\">Arts &amp; Culture</span><p class=\"title\n                            k-type-sub-header\">Music on the brink</p></div></a></div><div class=\"\n                k-promo promo-5 gel\"><a href=\"http://www.warcomposers.co.uk/\"><div class=\"media\"><img class=\"resp widescreen\" src=\"http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/256x144/p01sf4yf.jpg\" data-pid=\"p01sf4yf\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"k-g-sprite icon k-link\">Visit</span><span class=\"overlay\"></span></div><div class=\"context\"><p class=\"title\n                            k-type-sub-header\">Classical composers who fought in WWI</p></div></a>